  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Projects such as Launchpad provide some integration with upstream bug-trackers
(Trac, Mantis, Bugzilla etc.)

Shouldn't OpenHatch also be able to pull in bugs from upstream automagically?</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
